    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Broken linenumber after codeblok in Octopress]]></title>
    <link href="http://mohhasbias.github.com/blog/2014/02/22/broken-linenumber-after-codeblok/"/>
    <updated>2014-02-22T06:17:00+07:00</updated>
    <id>http://mohhasbias.github.com/blog/2014/02/22/broken-linenumber-after-codeblok</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>beberapa hari nyoba pakai linenumber dan codeblock di octopress selalu tidak berhasil.
browsing-browsing sampai nyasar ke repo-nya <a href="https://github.com/imathis/octopress">octopress</a>.
kesimpulannya, memang octopress belum support. masih mencari solusi yang clean (katanya <a href="https://github.com/imathis/octopress/pull/814">brandon imathis</a>).</p>

<p>Solusinya:
back to old working HTML</p>

<p>contoh:
jika menggunakan codeblock biasa:</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>1. bla bla bla
</span><span class='line'>  {% codeblock %}
</span><span class='line'>  ...
</span><span class='line'>  some code
</span><span class='line'>  ...
</span><span class='line'>  {% endcodeblock %}
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>2. bla bla bla lagi
</span><span class='line'>  {% codeblock %}
</span><span class='line'>  ...
</span><span class='line'>  programming is fun
</span><span class='line'>  ...
</span><span class='line'>  {% endcodeblock %}</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>akan menghasilkan:</p>

<ol>
<li>bla bla bla</li>
</ol>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>...
</span><span class='line'>  some code
</span><span class='line'>  ...</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ol>
<li>bla bla bla lagi</li>
</ol>


<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>...
</span><span class='line'>  programming is fun
</span><span class='line'>  ...</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>maka numberingnya akan rusak.
untuk membetulkannya, back to html</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
